WEBVTT

00:00:28.896 --> 00:00:32.886
Please welcome on stage, 
Mr. Umesh Sachdev.

00:00:32.940 --> 00:00:39.340
(Applause)

00:00:45.168 --> 00:00:46.744
Umesh Sachdev: This is Radha.

00:00:46.758 --> 00:00:49.744
She lives in a backward area of Bihar,

00:00:50.154 --> 00:00:53.674
and she wants to send Rs. 500 
to her daughter for Diwali.

00:00:53.968 --> 00:00:57.944
She is not educated enough to do it 
through internet banking,

00:00:58.208 --> 00:01:02.244
neither is there
any banking facility close to her village.